Package ServerSide.db

'db' package contains the classes that responsible on the communication with the database.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DbController
    DbController: A class which communicates with MySQL database.
    EntitiesResolver
    EntitiesResolver: A class that can resolve and create an List of instances of IEntity from received element.
    MessagesResolver
    MessagesResolver: An class that can resolve a Message to operation in the DB.
    QueryGenerator
    QueryGenerator: A factory of queries based on IEntity.

Package ServerSide.db Description

'db' package contains the classes that responsible on the communication with the database.

'Server' project contains all the functionality of the server side.
